{"word":"G3714 - ὀρεινός - oreinós - or-i-nos - Hill country","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀρεινός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">oreinós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">or-i-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hill country</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மலைநாடான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"mountainous, hilly, hill country"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3735 - ὄρος - óros - or'-os/3735\">G3735</a>; <i>mountainous</i>, that is, (feminine by implication of <a href=\"#/G5561 - χώρα - chṓra - kho'-rah/5561\">G5561</a>) the <i>Highlands</i> (of Judaea): - hill country.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}